Room.Name: Netherworld Lane
Room.ShortDescription: You are travelling along Netherworld Lane between Main and Marina Way.
Room.LongDescription: This small city block boasts two somewhat large buildings on both the north and south sides. The entrances to these buildings are located off of Main Street. Marina Way serves mostly as a back-road for the delivery of supplies and other accessories to these booming businesses. Marina Way is to the east and Main Street is to the west.
